formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x76_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>分别是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x77_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>后两个连通分支的点数。</p><p>证明：由 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20634-ref19">19</xref>] 的结果可知</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.20634-formula31"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x78_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>证毕。</p></sec><sec id="s4"><title>3. 主要结果</title><p>引理3.1. 若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x79_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，且<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x80_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，如图1 (<xref ref-type="fig" rid="fig1">Figure 1</xref>)所示，令<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x81_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>到<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x82_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的变换称为I-变换，则对任意正整数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x83_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x84_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>图1. 引理3.1中的I-变换</p><p>证明：由于树的每一条边都是割边，取<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x86_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则不妨设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x87_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的二个连通块的点数分别为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/10-1250527x88_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-for